short name for Liaoning 遼寧|辽宁[Liao2 ning2] province/Liao or Khitan dynasty (907-1125)
Liaoyuan prefecture-level city in Jilin province 吉林省 in northeast China

sentences.chinese: 遼源是一個不錯的地方。

sentences.english: It recently conducted surprise inspections in Liaoyuan, a city in Jilin Province, the newspaper reported.

sentences.english: I had worked in Liaoyuan for two years by the end of last month.
sentences.chinese: 到上月末爲止，我已經在遼源工作兩年了。
